title: Photos taken of possible footprints found on rural property near Albany
observed: Foot prints in the snow. I took some pictures. we had a moderate thaw, but we could see definite toes and a human-like shape, definitely bipedal.
location_details: 1 & 7/8ths of a mile off highway 84, on our rural property.
summary: Overcast throughout the day and breezy until evening.
